<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        .image {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1520px;
            height: 500px;
        }

        .button {
            position: absolute;
            top: 85%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-family: 'Book Antiqua', serif;
            background-color: #6f5045;
            color: white;
            border: 2px solid #000;
            border-radius: 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #a08674;
            color: black;
        }
        .featuresheader {
                font-family: 'Book Antiqua', serif;
                font-weight: bold;
                font-size: 35px;
                font-style: oblique;
                padding-left: 650px;
                font-weight: bold;
                color: #6f5045;
            }

            .featuresblocks {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center; 
        }

        .feature {
            flex: 1;
            margin-right: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column; 
            align-items: center; 
            text-align: center; 
        }

        .feature img {
            max-width: 120px; 
            height: auto; 
            margin-right: 10px; 
        }

        .feature p {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Book Antiqua', serif;
            color: #6f5045;
        }
        #featurep{
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .footer{
            background-color: #6f5045;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('navbar') %>
    <div class="image">
        <img src="images/hope_community.png" alt="">
        <a href="#" class="button">Donate</a>
    </div>
    <div class="featuresheader">
        <p>Our Features are</p>
    </div>
    <div class="featuresblocks">
        <div class="feature">
            <img src="images/feature1.png" alt="Feature 1">
            <p id="featurep"> <strong>Direct Help</strong></p><br>
            <p> Users can create profiles to connect <br>with donors or recipients, facilitating <br> direct assistance and support.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <img src="images/feature2.png" alt="Feature 2">
            <p id="featurep"><strong>Giving Information</strong></p><br>
            <p>Recipients can list specific needs, such <br> as essentials or educational support, enabling <br>donors to address them directly and effectively.                </p>
        </div>
    </div><br><br>
    <div class="footer">
        <footer>
            <p>all rights reservered @2024</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>